Unless otherwise indicated, all dollar amounts in this annual report on Form 40-F are in United States dollars. The exchange rate of United States dollars into Canadian dollars, on December 31, 2024 based upon the rate of exchange as quoted by the Bank of Canada, was USD $1.00 = CAD $1.4389.
